# This directory holds captured SBF binary fixtures used by replay tests
# (Phase 3+).  At Phase 2B it intentionally contains only this placeholder.
#
# Fixtures will include:
#   ext_sensor_meas.sbf          one valid IMU frame
#   meas_epoch_30sv.sbf          MeasEpoch with 30 satellites in view
#   meas_epoch_corrupt_crc.sbf   same frame with one bit flipped in body
#   meas_epoch_truncated.sbf     frame missing trailing bytes
#   measepoch_oversize.sbf       declared Length > kMaxSbfLength (DoS guard)
#
